# podcast-local — this repo tracks only the debug / documentation artifacts.
# The site itself (app/), Local's runtime folders (conf/, logs/), MCP scratch output,
# and editor/tool config are intentionally NOT tracked.
#
# Strategy: ignore everything at the root, then explicitly allow the artifacts.

/*

!/.gitignore
!/.gitattributes
!/README.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/handover.md
!/.mcp.json
!/tasks/
!/accessibility-fixes/
